title: At least 20 injured in Florida school shooting: media
text:
At least 20 injured in Florida school shooting: media Wednesday, February 14, 2018 - 00:42 
The Broward County sheriff says a shooter is still at large at a Florida high school after at least 20 people have been injured. Rough Cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
